OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of being
OL,7,Finvolved with the theft of a #4.75m
OL,8,Fgold toilet from Blenheim Palace in
OL,9,FOxfordshire.
OL,11,FThe "audacious" raid at the birthplace
OL,12,Fof Winston Churchill was carried out
OL,13,Fin the early hours of 14 September
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FThe toilet, which was created by
OL,17,FItalian artist Maurizio Cattelan, was
OL,18,Fa star attraction in an exhibition
OL,19,Fwhen it was stolen by sledgehammer-
OL,20,Fwielding thieves who smashed their way
OL,21,Finto the palace.
