OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FThieves drove through locked, wooden
OL,7,Fgates into the grounds of the palace
OL,8,Fbefore breaking in through a window.
OL,10,FIn total, the theft took just five
OL,11,Fminutes and palace security guards
OL,12,Fchased the fleeing cars on foot.
OL,14,FIt is believed the 98kg artwork has
OL,15,Fnow been split up and disposed of,
OL,16,FOxford Crown Court was told during the
OL,17,Ftrial.
OL,19,FOne man, James Sheen, was previously
OL,20,Fhanded a 17-year sentence after
OL,21,Fpleading guilty to burglary.
