OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FHe allegedly took the 20 kilos of gold
OL,7,Ffrom the toilet artwork to Birmingham
OL,8,FJewellery Quarter on 27 September
OL,9,F2019, and sold it for #26,000 a
OL,10,Fkilogram ` pocketing a total of
OL,11,F#520,000, the court heard.
OL,13,FSheen's DNA was found both on a
OL,14,Fsledgehammer left at the scene and in
OL,15,Fthe stolen Isuzu truck used in the
OL,16,Fraid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
