OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FTracksuit bottoms seized at his home
OL,7,Fhad hundreds of gold fragments on
OL,8,Fthem, which when analysed were
OL,9,Findistinguishable from the gold from
OL,10,Fwhich the toilet was made.
OL,12,FSheen, from Wellingborough,
OL,13,FNorthamptonshire, also pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto an offence of transferring or
OL,15,Fconverting gold in Birmingham on that
OL,16,Fdate.
