OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FThe jury at Oxford Crown Court found
OL,7,FMichael Jones, 39 from Oxford, guilty
OL,8,Fof burglary, with the prosecution
OL,9,Fsaying he was there on the night of
OL,10,Fthe raid alongside Sheen.
OL,12,FJones worked with Sheen as a roofer
OL,13,Fand builder, and went on
OL,14,Freconnaissance missions for Sheen -
OL,15,Fvisiting the Palace twice. The second
OL,16,Ftime, the day before the gold toilet
OL,17,Fwas stolen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
