OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FMembers of the public booked slots to
OL,7,Fuse the toilet, with Jones taking
OL,8,Fpictures recording his time in there.
OL,9,FA selfie, alongside the lock and the
OL,10,Fwindow later broken to steal the
OL,11,Ftoilet, was also used as evidence to
OL,12,Fshow he was there on a mission for
OL,13,FSheen.
OL,15,FQuestioned if he "took advantage of"
OL,16,Fthe gold toilet's "facilities", he
OL,17,Ftold the court that he did make use of
OL,18,Fit and it was "splendid".
