OL,6,FFred Doe, 36, from Windsor, has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of conspiracy to transfer
OL,8,Fcriminal property.
OL,10,FBora Guccuk, 41, from West London, has
OL,11,Fbeen found not guilty of conspiracy to
OL,12,Ftransfer criminal property.
OL,14,FDoe and Jones will be sentenced at a
OL,15,Flater date.
