OL,3,CTwo men guilty in Blenheim Palace gold
OL,4,Ctoilet theft case
OL,6,FShan Saunders of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService said: "This was an audacious
OL,8,Fraid which had been carefully planned
OL,9,Fand executed ` but those responsible
OL,10,Fwere not careful enough, leaving a
OL,11,Ftrail of evidence in the form of
OL,12,Fforensics, CCTV footage and phone data.
OL,14,F"It has been a complex case to
OL,15,Fprosecute, involving a nationwide
OL,16,Finvestigation with many lines of
OL,17,Finquiry to identify those who were
OL,18,Fsubsequently charged in relation to
OL,19,Fthe theft.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
